<h2><a name='sect0' href='#toc0'>Name</a></h2>
<p>
pevent - Generate an event and inject it into the system
<h2><a name='sect1' href='#toc1'>Synopsis</a></h2>
<br>
<pre>

</pre>
<h2><a name='sect2' href='#toc2'>C]pevent [ options ]R]Description</a></h2>
<p>
C]peventR]
<dl>

<dt>will generate a specified event
and inject it into a </dt>
<dd>server. This requires that C]peventR] connect to an
appropriate server - the tool will automatically attempt to do so, but options
are provided to assist its search or to direct it to a specific server.
</dd>
</dl>

<h2><a name='sect3' href='#toc3'>Options</a></h2>
<p>
C]peventR] supports the following options: <br>
<pre>

</pre>
